Package edu.rit.util

Package edu.rit.util contains general utility components.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Action<T>
    Interface Action specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target object.
    ActionResult<T,R>
    Interface ActionResult specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target object and that returns some result.
    DoubleAction
    Interface DoubleAction specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target double precision floating point number.
    DoubleActionResult<R>
    Interface DoubleActionResult specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target double precision floating point number and that returns some result.

    Interface DoublePredicate specifies the interface for an object that performs some Boolean test on some target double precision floating point number.
    FloatAction
    Interface FloatAction specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target single precision floating point number.
    FloatActionResult<R>
    Interface FloatActionResult specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target single precision floating point number and that returns some result.
    FloatPredicate
    Interface FloatPredicate specifies the interface for an object that performs some Boolean test on some target single precision floating point number.
    IntAction
    Interface IntAction specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target integer.
    IntActionResult<R>
    Interface IntActionResult specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target integer and that returns some result.
    IntPredicate
    Interface IntPredicate specifies the interface for an object that performs some Boolean test on some target integer (type int).
    Logger
    Interface Logger specifies the interface for an object that logs messages.
    LongAction
    Interface LongAction specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target long integer.
    LongActionResult<R>
    Interface LongActionResult specifies the interface for an object that performs some action on some target long integer and that returns some result.
    LongPredicate
    Interface LongPredicate specifies the interface for an object that performs some Boolean test on some target long integer (type long).
    Predicate<T>
    Interface Predicate specifies the interface for an object that performs some Boolean test on some target object.
